# RustIRC Version 0.3.8 Release
# Released: August 26, 2025
# 
# Enhanced Iced Material Design GUI - 100% Complete
# 
# Major Achievements:
# - Complete Material Design 3 implementation with ZERO compilation errors
# - Fixed Material Demo scrollable widget panic issue
